      <description><![CDATA[<h2>0.2.0</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Non-public posts are now end-to-end encrypted: only the audience you pick (a Circle, or your friend-of-friend graph) can read them, including any photos or video attached.</li>
  <li>Backups now carry attached media, not just post data.</li>
  <li>Dependency and packaging maintenance: updated p2panda, patched a transitive RUSTSEC advisory, and cleaned up stray licensing files.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
